fields.name: Shelly
fields.description: Shelly's spread-fire shotgun blasts the other team with buckshot. Her Super destroys cover and keeps her opponents at a distance!

fields.name: Nita
fields.description: Nita strikes her enemies with a thunderous shockwave. Her Super summons a massive bear to fight by her side!

fields.name: Colt
fields.description: Colt fires an accurate burst of bullets from his dual revolvers. His Super shreds cover and extends the bullet barrage!

fields.name: Bull
fields.description: Bull deals massive damage up close with his shotgun. For his Super move, he charges through barriers and knocks back enemies!

fields.name: Jessie
fields.description: Jessie's Shock Rifle shoots energy orbs that bounce between enemies. Her Super deploys a cute but deadly gun turret!

fields.name: Brock
fields.description: Brock fires a long-range, explosive rocket at enemies. His Super is a ballistic rocket barrage that destroys cover!

fields.name: Dynamike
fields.description: Dynamike lobs two explosive sticks of dynamite. His Super attack is a whole barrel full of dynamite that blows up cover!

fields.name: Bo
fields.description: Bo fires three explosive arrows toward his targets. His Super ability places a trio of hidden, explosive mines on the ground!

fields.name: Tick
fields.description: Tick is a metal ball of barely controlled excitement and energy - explosive energy! He throws mines, and his Super makes his head detach, seek a target and explode.

fields.name: 8-Bit
fields.description: 8-Bit lumbers along like an arcade cabinet on legs. He shoots Blaster Beams and his Super boosts friendlies' damage!

fields.name: Emz
fields.description: Emz attacks with blasts of hair spray that deal damage over time, and slows down opponents with her Super.

fields.name: El Primo
fields.description: El Primo throws a flurry of punches at his enemies. His Super is a leaping elbow drop that deals damage to all caught underneath!

fields.name: Barley
fields.description: Barley attacks by lobbing bottles at enemies, doing splash damage. His Super is a huge barrage of burning bottles!

fields.name: Poco
fields.description: Poco fires damaging sound waves at enemies. His Super can heal both Poco himself and his teammates!

fields.name: Rosa
fields.description: This boxing botanist will plant her feet and go toe to toe! Her Super gives her tough, vegan protective gear.

fields.name: Rico
fields.description: Rico fires a burst of bullets that bounce off walls. His Super burst is a long barrage of bouncy bullets that pierce targets!

fields.name: Darryl
fields.description: Darryl has a powerful double-shotgun attack. His Super move is a reckless roll inside his bouncy barrel!

fields.name: Penny
fields.description: Penny shoots bags of coins, damaging the target and anyone standing behind. Her Super is a mortar-style cannon turret!

fields.name: Carl
fields.description: Carl throws his Pickaxe like a boomerang. His Super is a crazy cart spin that clobbers anyone around him.

fields.name: Jacky
fields.description: Jacky works her Jackhammer to shake up the ground and nearby enemies. Her Super pulls in nearby foes, leaving them in the dust!

fields.name: Piper
fields.description: Piper's sniper shots do more damage the farther they travel. Her Super drops grenades at her feet, while Piper herself leaps away!

fields.name: Pam
fields.description: Pam shoots from the hip, peppering targets with shrapnel. Her Super is a healing turret that restores her and teammates' health!

fields.name: Frank
fields.description: Frank swings his hammer at enemies, sending a shockwave. His Super is an especially powerful blow that stuns enemies!

fields.name: Bibi
fields.description: Batter up! Bibi's got a sweet swing that can knock back enemies when her Home Run bar is charged. Her Super is a bouncing ball of gum that deals damage.

fields.name: Bea
fields.description: Bea loves bugs and hugs. She shoots her mechanical drones at range, and her Super sends forth an angry army of swarming bees!

fields.name: Nani
fields.description: Nani loves her friends and looks over them with a watchful lens. She handles threats with angled shots, and her Super allows Nani to commandeer her pal Peep, who goes out with a bang!

fields.name: Mortis
fields.description: Mortis dashes forward with each swing of his shovel. As his Super attack, he sends a cloud of bats to damage enemies and heal himself!

fields.name: Tara
fields.description: Tara's triple tarot card attack pierces through enemies. Her Super is a black hole that sucks in all nearby enemies, causing damage!

fields.name: Gene
fields.description: Gene uses his magic lamp to shoot a splitting projectile. His super is a magical hand that grabs and pulls enemies close!

fields.name: Max
fields.description: Max goes fast! Her attack is a fast-firing blaster. Her Super speeds up her and allies!

fields.name: Mr. P
fields.description: Mr. P is a disgruntled luggage handler who angrily hurls suitcases at opponents. His Super calls robo-porters to help him.

fields.name: Sprout
fields.description: Sprout was built to plant life, launching bouncy Seed Bombs with reckless love. Its Super creates a plant-based obstacle!

fields.name: Spike
fields.description: Spike throws cactus grenades that send needles flying, and a show-stopping Super: a field of cactus spines that slows down and damages enemies!

fields.name: Crow
fields.description: Crow fires a trio of poisoned daggers. As a Super move he leaps, firing daggers both on jump and on landing!

fields.name: Leon
fields.description: Leon shoots a quick salvo of blades at his target. His Super trick is a smoke bomb that makes him invisible for a little while!

fields.name: Sandy
fields.description: Sandy is a sleep-deprived Brawler with powerful control over sand: casting sharp pebbles at enemies, and summoning a sandstorm to hide teammates.

fields.name: Amber
fields.description: Amber has always been a firebug. She loves to light up the world and any opponents that come at her!

fields.name: Gale
fields.description: Gale is a tireless handyman who gets no rest. He blasts foes with a wide shot of wind and snow and his Super pushes them back with a huge gust of wind!

fields.name: Surge
fields.description: He's a Protector with a penchant for parties. Surge attacks foes with energy drink blasts that split in two on contact. His Super upgrades his stats in 3 stages and comes complete with totally awesome body mods!

fields.name: Colette
fields.description: Colette is going to get you! She taxes opponents' health and has fancy moves to boot.
